{"tid":1562524,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"915民陣數唔到人數，連登自己公佈人數。","createTime":"2019-09-12T04:51:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T06:21:35.000Z","uid":189799,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e5803075269266a8a5f9af6eef9bdb7c04b1b523","tid":1562524,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:51:52.000Z","msg":"818 黑警只批集會，民陣玩流水集會，最後有170萬人。<br />\n<br />\n宜家黑警連集會都唔批，係唔想民陣又可以公佈百萬人參加，證明到仲有好撚多人唔收貨。<br />\n<br />\n915不如連登自己公佈人數，人數嘅真確性其實多人講就得，到時個個post都話有2百萬人。多人講，多報導，之後啲人就會話915二百萬人堅持五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n就好似69一百萬，616二百萬，果陣啲藍絲都話無咁多。宜家啲報導都只會話69有一百萬，所以915之後連登自己宣傳915有二百萬人（數字可以因應情況而改變），宣傳力度夠大，就越多人相信。"},{"pid":"1fdf1788d2e52dc00c1af1a14470120e1b4a5770","tid":1562524,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:52:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"5326c5637d82f009901250046cba47a76ab30d0d","tid":1562524,"uid":13774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:52:20.000Z","msg":"民記<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597583b71cfba67756f4eedfddc385861db19d44","tid":1562524,"uid":134774,"li